  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的控制流程图。起点是PLC逻辑控制器，它要跟MQTT Broker通信，然后Broker把指令发给执行器控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，PLC作为起始节点，通过MQTT Broker中转。那Broker到执行器控制器之间是什么关系？是一对一还是一对多？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Broker后面应该有个决策点，执行器控制器需要根据条件分流。另外还要有一条分支去遥测数据流，用于监控。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：PLC → Broker → 决策节点，然后从决策节点分出三条路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "PLC到Broker的那条连线要标注一下，代表获取资金或者资源分配的信号，写\"Get money\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加标注。现在决策节点后面有三个出口，分别去两个执行器控制器和遥测流，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但两个执行器控制器的命名我确认一下——它们其实是同一种设备，只是实例不同，都叫ActuatorController就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我注意到一个问题：决策节点C和后面的D节点标签重复了，都是ActuatorController。我需要把决策节点改成菱形判断符号，后面两个用方框表示具体实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "修复得好。那三条分支的标注我来定：去第一个执行器的标\"One\"，第二个标\"Two\"，去遥测流的标\"Three\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部标注完成。现在结构是：PLC_Logic → [Get money] → MQTT_Broker → 判断节点 → One/Two/Three 分别指向两个ActuatorController和TelemetryStream。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "结构正确。遥测流那个分支是独立的数据上报通道，不依赖执行器的状态反馈，这样设计符合我们的架构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认最终版本：TD布局，PLC起始，经MQTT中转，决策后三分支，标注清晰。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
